{
  "stem": "9878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All my brothers and sisters attended religious schools, the yeshivas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister attended a, a, a girls' school, and the boys attended boys' school because the, the religious schools were segregated, boys separate and girls separate.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was a housewife.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She stayed home and made sure that we have something to eat, and there was some food at home, of course.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, since we were the majority of kids in the city, in my hometown, there was not too much problem with the kids.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was incidents where I was beaten up by, by a Gentile kid, just simply because I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we kept together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went home from school together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when I went to school, I was a strong kid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So all the children wait for me to come home with [LAUGHS] them in order that I should be able to-- because by us, the fights were only fistfights.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were no knives or guns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This didn't exist, only fistfights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You got a beating, got a black eye, but this is all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But if you are a good athlete and a good-- like I was-- a good ballplayer, soccer player-- I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whatever they played in a group, and they needed extra kids, they even took the Jewish kids in to play.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they were very much in favor for athletic kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were-- we got along.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I spoke Polish fluently, as good as the Poles did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we got along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But there was prejudices, quietly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we, we took it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is the way it's supposed to be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We are foreigners.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we took it the way life has continued this way.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
